{ Statements

   Get log entries that were written by the most recently started task:
code {
select *
from
   log_v
where
   task_exec_id = (select max(id) from task_exec);
code }

}

sa:
  `LOG_MGMT` depends on → development/databases/Oracle/PL-SQL/libs/personal/task[`TASK`]
